name: 3D Test (Cosmos89)
description:
In this 3D test made in Unity, the player can do attack, jump, roll, run fast and bend. I put an enemy with bar-life  that attack and fall when knocked down. All with sound effects and this located in a world of nature...

You can jump to the last plataform and get the sward for make more damage.

Animations from Mixamo.com
